settings.description: Demake of the first level of the fangame smbddx
You sneak into Boom Boom's Japanese castle in Kyoto like an cool guy, and you have to defeat him!
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.

ok this level will not be trash i promise
